---
import PrototypeLayout from '../../layouts/PrototypeLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/prototypes/design-leadership-obduction.css';

const pageTitle = 'The Plate Tectonics of Design Leadership — Tectonic Cross-Section';
const pageDescription =
  'A cross-section of design leadership geology: Stage I Initial Uplift, Stage II Sustained Thrust, and Stage III New Mountain Range.';
const fonts =
  'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,300;9..144,400;9..144,500;9..144,600;9..144,700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap';
---

<PrototypeLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} fonts={fonts}>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="eyebrow">— Issue 302 · The Plate Tectonics of Design Leadership —</div>
      <h1>Tectonic Cross-Section</h1>
      <div class="subtitle">Three stages in one geology: compress, thrust, grow — hover each zone in order.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="diagram-wrap diagram-epoch">
      <div class="legend">
        <div class="legend-item rust" data-stage="1">
          <div class="key"><span class="swatch" style="background:#a8442a"></span>Stage I · Initial Uplift</div>
          <div class="body">First contact between AI-native and incumbent models. Pressure builds at the edges; nothing dramatic at the surface yet. Incumbents still in charge — boards hire the previous archetype. <em>The wedge is beneath.</em></div>
        </div>
        <div class="legend-item teal" data-stage="2">
          <div class="key"><span class="swatch" style="background:#2d5d63"></span>Stage II · Sustained Thrust</div>
          <div class="body">The override plate gains momentum — hover to thrust left and compress the crust. Pressure builds at the collision zone, lifting the range above. <em>Horizontal force becomes vertical terrain.</em></div>
        </div>
        <div class="legend-item gold" data-stage="3">
          <div class="key"><span class="swatch" style="background:#b8893d"></span>Stage III · New Mountain Range</div>
          <div class="body">The range rests on the override plate — low foothills at first, visible but not yet dominant. Hover to grow the terrain slowly into full relief. <em>When the new normal no longer needs a label.</em></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="diagram-canvas">
        <div class="stage-popovers" aria-live="polite">
          <div class="stage-popover stage-popover--rust" data-stage="1" id="friction-stage-1" role="tooltip">
            <div class="stage-popover__tag">Friction zone · 01</div>
            <div class="stage-popover__num">CRAFT TRANSMISSION</div>
            <div class="stage-popover__title">Who develops the next generation when succession is thinning?</div>
            <div class="stage-popover__desc">The pipeline isn't looking great. High-potential future leaders need mentorship — but they need to trust you understand their craft before they'll accept your perspective on AI.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stage-popover stage-popover--teal" data-stage="2" id="friction-stage-2" role="tooltip">
            <div class="stage-popover__tag">Friction zone · 02</div>
            <div class="stage-popover__num">CREDENTIALING LAG</div>
            <div class="stage-popover__title">Boards still hire for the last decade's archetype.</div>
            <div class="stage-popover__desc">Standard credentialing feels lagging while market validation emerges. The summit forms faster than the org chart updates — mid-career leaders carry the new model into rooms still scoring the old one.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stage-popover stage-popover--gold" data-stage="3" id="friction-stage-3" role="tooltip">
            <div class="stage-popover__tag">Friction zone · 03</div>
            <div class="stage-popover__num">MELT-ZONE TALENT</div>
            <div class="stage-popover__title">Adapt, resist, or become irrelevant?</div>
            <div class="stage-popover__desc">Designers get submerged into the molten lava of irrelevance — recycled into founding roles, back to IC, or out of the industry. In the best case, experience becomes material for the multi-modal generations.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      <svg class="cross-section" viewBox="0 0 1200 660" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet">
        <defs>
          <linearGradient id="skyG" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#c8d4e0" stop-opacity="0.35"/>
            <stop offset="55%" stop-color="#d4dbc8" stop-opacity="0.55"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#f1e9d8" stop-opacity="0"/>
          </linearGradient>

          <radialGradient id="cloudSoft" cx="0.5" cy="0.5" r="0.5">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#f1e9d8" stop-opacity="0.85"/>
            <stop offset="70%" stop-color="#e8e4d8" stop-opacity="0.35"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#f1e9d8" stop-opacity="0"/>
          </radialGradient>

          <linearGradient id="subPlate" x1="180" y1="340" x2="900" y2="760" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#c89456" stop-opacity="0.82"/>
            <stop offset="42%" stop-color="#a8442a" stop-opacity="0.78"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#5a2818" stop-opacity="0.9"/>
          </linearGradient>

          <!-- overriding plate (AI-native, teal) - riding on top -->
          <linearGradient id="overPlate" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#7aa5ab" stop-opacity="0.95"/>
            <stop offset="50%" stop-color="#2d5d63" stop-opacity="0.9"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#1a3d42" stop-opacity="0.95"/>
          </linearGradient>
          <linearGradient id="overSurface" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#a8c4c8" stop-opacity="0.6"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#5a8a90" stop-opacity="0.3"/>
          </linearGradient>

          <!-- mantle / asthenosphere — warm at collision, deep brown below -->
          <linearGradient id="mantleG" x1="0" y1="400" x2="0" y2="660" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#8a5238" stop-opacity="0.52"/>
            <stop offset="28%" stop-color="#b85a32" stop-opacity="0.48"/>
            <stop offset="55%" stop-color="#a8442a" stop-opacity="0.55"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#2a2218" stop-opacity="0.92"/>
          </linearGradient>

          <linearGradient id="asthenosphereGlow" x1="480" y1="420" x2="920" y2="660" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#e87a3a" stop-opacity="0.22"/>
            <stop offset="45%" stop-color="#c44e28" stop-opacity="0.38"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#5a2818" stop-opacity="0"/>
          </linearGradient>

          <linearGradient id="subLimbFade" x1="580" y1="480" x2="960" y2="780" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#a8442a" stop-opacity="0"/>
            <stop offset="55%" stop-color="#c45e28" stop-opacity="0.28"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#e87a3a" stop-opacity="0.55"/>
          </linearGradient>

          <linearGradient id="magmaVeinG" x1="780" y1="640" x2="540" y2="400" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#e87a3a" stop-opacity="0.85"/>
            <stop offset="55%" stop-color="#c44e28" stop-opacity="0.55"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#a8442a" stop-opacity="0.15"/>
          </linearGradient>

          <radialGradient id="mantleMeltFade" cx="620" cy="520" r="120" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#a8442a" stop-opacity="0.28"/>
            <stop offset="55%" stop-color="#7a3820" stop-opacity="0.14"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#2a2218" stop-opacity="0"/>
          </radialGradient>

          <linearGradient id="peakG" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#d4a857" stop-opacity="1"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#8a6628" stop-opacity="0.9"/>
          </linearGradient>
          <linearGradient id="peakG2" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#c49a4a" stop-opacity="1"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7a5a22" stop-opacity="0.9"/>
          </linearGradient>
          <linearGradient id="peakG3" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#b8893d" stop-opacity="0.95"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#6e5420" stop-opacity="0.85"/>
          </linearGradient>

          <linearGradient id="rangeShelfG" x1="0" y1="1" x2="0" y2="0">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#5a8a90" stop-opacity="1"/>
            <stop offset="28%" stop-color="#7aa5ab" stop-opacity="0.98"/>
            <stop offset="58%" stop-color="#9a7530" stop-opacity="0.96"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#c49a4a" stop-opacity="0.95"/>
          </linearGradient>

          <!-- melting / heat glow at subduction zone -->
          <radialGradient id="melt" cx="0.5" cy="0.5" r="0.5">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#a8442a" stop-opacity="0.45"/>
            <stop offset="60%" stop-color="#7a3820" stop-opacity="0.18"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#5a2818" stop-opacity="0"/>
          </radialGradient>

          <radialGradient id="meltPool" cx="0.45" cy="0.55" r="0.55">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#e87a3a" stop-opacity="0.95"/>
            <stop offset="55%" stop-color="#c44e28" stop-opacity="0.65"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#5a2818" stop-opacity="0"/>
          </radialGradient>

          <radialGradient id="lavaFluid" cx="0.45" cy="0.5" r="0.6">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#c89456" stop-opacity="0.55"/>
            <stop offset="35%" stop-color="#a8442a" stop-opacity="0.42"/>
            <stop offset="70%" stop-color="#7a3820" stop-opacity="0.22"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#5a2818" stop-opacity="0"/>
          </radialGradient>

          <filter id="smokeSoft" x="-40%" y="-40%" width="180%" height="180%">
            <feGaussianBlur in="SourceGraphic" stdDeviation="2.5"/>
          </filter>

          <filter id="lavaSoft" x="-30%" y="-30%" width="160%" height="160%">
            <feGaussianBlur in="SourceGraphic" stdDeviation="4" result="blur"/>
            <feMerge>
              <feMergeNode in="blur"/>
            </feMerge>
          </filter>

          <clipPath id="magmaClip" clipPathUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <path d="
              M 470 380
              L 552 468
              L 680 580
              L 860 720
              L 980 810
              L 1200 660
              L 1200 480
              L 700 480
              L 620 470
              L 560 450
              L 500 420
              L 470 380 Z"/>
          </clipPath>
        </defs>

        <!-- sky -->
        <rect x="0" y="0" width="1200" height="140" fill="url(#skyG)"/>
        <g class="sky-clouds" pointer-events="none" opacity="0.55">
          <ellipse cx="180" cy="52" rx="72" ry="18" fill="url(#cloudSoft)"/>
          <ellipse cx="248" cy="48" rx="48" ry="14" fill="url(#cloudSoft)"/>
          <ellipse cx="920" cy="38" rx="88" ry="20" fill="url(#cloudSoft)"/>
          <ellipse cx="1020" cy="44" rx="56" ry="15" fill="url(#cloudSoft)"/>
        </g>

        <!-- MANTLE — behind crust; top surface meets subducting limb, warms into melt zone -->
        <g class="mantle-zone" pointer-events="none">
          <path
            class="mantle-fill"
            d="
              M 0 660
              L 1200 660
              L 1200 480
              L 700 480
              L 620 470
              L 560 450
              L 500 420
              L 470 380
              L 552 468
              L 650 535
              L 720 590
              L 800 660
              L 880 730
              L 960 810
              L 620 550
              L 498 428
              L 440 440
              L 280 425
              L 0 420
              L 0 660 Z"
            fill="url(#mantleG)"
          />
          <path
            class="mantle-melt-fade"
            d="
              M 470 380
              L 505 418
              L 552 468
              L 498 428
              L 440 440
              L 470 380 Z"
            fill="url(#mantleMeltFade)"
          />
          <path
            class="asthenosphere-glow"
            d="
              M 470 380
              L 552 468
              L 650 535
              L 800 660
              L 1200 660
              L 1200 480
              L 700 480
              L 620 470
              L 560 450
              L 500 420
              L 470 380 Z"
            fill="url(#asthenosphereGlow)"
          />
          <text
            class="mantle-layer-label"
            x="1040"
            y="598"
            text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace"
            font-size="9"
            letter-spacing="2"
            fill="#f1e9d8"
            opacity="0.42"
          >ASTHENOSPHERE</text>

          <!-- Magma conduit — behind crust; clipped to mantle wedge only -->
          <g class="magma-conduit" clip-path="url(#magmaClip)" pointer-events="none">
            <path
              class="magma-vein magma-vein--primary"
              d="M 820 648 C 760 580, 680 500, 590 430 C 560 408, 538 398, 520 388"
              fill="none"
              stroke="url(#magmaVeinG)"
              stroke-width="5"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              opacity="0.42"
            />
            <path
              class="magma-vein magma-vein--branch"
              d="M 720 560 C 660 480, 580 420, 510 395"
              fill="none"
              stroke="url(#magmaVeinG)"
              stroke-width="3"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              opacity="0.22"
            />
          </g>
        </g>

        <!-- STAGE I · INITIAL UPLIFT -->
        <g class="stage-one-zone">
          <g class="subducting-body" pointer-events="none">
            <g class="subducting-plate">
            <path d="
              M 0 280
              L 0 420
              L 280 425
              L 440 440
              L 498 428
              L 552 468
              L 650 535
              L 720 590
              L 790 645
              L 860 700
              L 930 755
              L 980 795
              L 930 710
              L 880 660
              L 830 610
              L 800 580
              L 740 510
              L 660 450
              L 538 408
              L 498 428
              L 380 385
              L 200 375
              L 0 372
              L 0 280 Z"
              fill="url(#subPlate)"
              stroke="none"/>

            <path d="
              M 0 280
              L 200 282
              L 380 290
              L 540 310
              L 660 350
              L 740 410
              L 498 428
              L 380 385
              L 200 375
              L 0 372 Z"
              fill="#c89456"
              fill-opacity="0.2"/>

            <path class="subducting-strata" d="M 0 320 L 200 322 L 380 332 L 540 360 L 620 398 L 688 448" fill="none" stroke="#5a2818" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.5" stroke-dasharray="4 6"/>
            <path class="subducting-strata subducting-strata--delay" d="M 0 350 L 200 350 L 380 358 L 540 388 L 620 428 L 688 478" fill="none" stroke="#5a2818" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.5" stroke-dasharray="4 6"/>
            <path class="subducting-strata subducting-strata--limb" d="M 548 448 L 618 502 L 688 556 L 758 610" fill="none" stroke="#5a2818" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.45" stroke-dasharray="4 6"/>
            <path class="subducting-downdip" d="M 420 360 L 500 410 L 552 468 L 620 522 L 688 576 L 758 630" fill="none" stroke="#f1e9d8" stroke-width="0.7" opacity="0.22" stroke-dasharray="3 9"/>
            <path class="subducting-downdip subducting-downdip--delay" d="M 460 395 L 528 442 L 598 498 L 668 552 L 738 606" fill="none" stroke="#f1e9d8" stroke-width="0.7" opacity="0.16" stroke-dasharray="3 9"/>

            <!-- Slab limb dissolves into asthenosphere (textbook fade) -->
            <path
              class="subducting-limb-fade"
              d="
                M 552 468
                L 650 535
                L 720 590
                L 790 645
                L 860 700
                L 930 755
                L 980 795
                L 960 810
                L 880 730
                L 800 660
                L 720 590
                L 650 535
                L 552 468 Z"
              fill="url(#subLimbFade)"
            />
            </g>

            <g class="subducting-sink" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle class="sink-particle" cx="500" cy="390" r="2.5" fill="#c89456"/>
              <circle class="sink-particle sink-particle--2" cx="560" cy="420" r="2" fill="#a8442a"/>
              <circle class="sink-particle sink-particle--3" cx="620" cy="455" r="2.5" fill="#c89456"/>
              <circle class="sink-particle sink-particle--4" cx="680" cy="495" r="2" fill="#8a3d28"/>
              <circle class="sink-particle sink-particle--5" cx="430" cy="365" r="2" fill="#a8442a"/>
              <circle class="sink-particle sink-particle--6" cx="720" cy="555" r="2" fill="#a8442a"/>
              <circle class="sink-particle sink-particle--7" cx="800" cy="615" r="2.5" fill="#8a3d28"/>
            </g>
          </g>

          <!-- In-plate strata labels — textbook layer style (no leaders) -->
          <g class="subducting-labels" pointer-events="none">
            <text class="subducting-label" x="280" y="318" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" letter-spacing="1.5" fill="#1a1410" opacity="0.88">STAFFING RESOURCES</text>
            <text class="subducting-label" x="280" y="354" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" letter-spacing="1.5" fill="#1a1410" opacity="0.78">LAGGING WAYS OF WORK</text>
            <text class="subducting-label" x="280" y="392" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" letter-spacing="1.5" fill="#1a1410" opacity="0.68">PREVIOUS ERA PLAYBOOKS</text>
            <text class="subducting-label subducting-label--layer" x="140" y="408" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="8" letter-spacing="2" fill="#1a1410" opacity="0.52">LITHOSPHERE</text>
          </g>

          <g class="subducting-callout" pointer-events="none">
            <line x1="120" y1="282" x2="120" y2="138" stroke="#1a1410" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-dasharray="2 3"/>
            <circle cx="120" cy="282" r="3" fill="#1a1410"/>
            <text x="120" y="128" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fraunces, serif" font-style="italic" font-weight="500" font-size="20" fill="#1a1410">Stage I · Initial Uplift</text>
            <text x="120" y="108" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" letter-spacing="2" fill="#a8442a">— HOVER TO COMPRESS —</text>
          </g>

          <rect
            class="stage-one-hit"
            x="0"
            y="190"
            width="580"
            height="380"
            fill="transparent"
            pointer-events="all"
            aria-hidden="true"
          />
        </g>

        <!-- STAGE II · SUSTAINED THRUST -->
        <g class="stage-two-zone">
          <g class="stage-two-plate" pointer-events="none">
            <path
              class="override-plate"
              d="
                M 1200 235
                L 1200 480
                L 700 480
                L 620 470
                L 560 450
                L 500 420
                L 470 380
                L 460 340
                L 470 290
                L 490 250
                L 530 220
                L 600 200
                L 700 195
                L 850 205
                L 1000 215
                L 1200 235 Z"
              fill="url(#overPlate)"
              stroke="#1a1410"
              stroke-width="1.5"
            />

            <path
              class="override-surface"
              d="
                M 1200 235
                L 1000 215
                L 850 205
                L 700 195
                L 600 200
                L 530 220
                L 490 250
                L 530 235
                L 600 215
                L 700 210
                L 850 218
                L 1000 230
                L 1200 250 Z"
              fill="url(#overSurface)"
            />

            <!-- Stage III foundation — welded to the override surface, under thrust front -->
            <g class="stage-three-anchor" pointer-events="none">
              <path
                class="range-buttress"
                d="M 332 278 L 332 328 L 448 342 L 458 318 L 470 290 L 398 268 Z"
                fill="url(#overPlate)"
                stroke="#1a1410"
                stroke-width="1.2"
              />
              <path
                class="range-shadow"
                d="M 332 278 L 468 293 L 490 253 L 530 238 L 600 218 L 700 213 L 850 221"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#1a3d42"
                stroke-width="4"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                opacity="0.22"
              />
              <path
                class="range-shelf"
                d="
                  M 332 278
                  L 398 268
                  L 470 290
                  L 490 250
                  L 530 235
                  L 600 215
                  L 700 210
                  L 850 218
                  L 842 218
                  L 842 200
                  L 850 200
                  L 700 192
                  L 600 197
                  L 530 217
                  L 490 232
                  L 470 268
                  L 398 250
                  L 332 302
                  L 332 328
                  L 448 342
                  L 458 318
                  Z"
                fill="url(#rangeShelfG)"
                stroke="#1a1410"
                stroke-width="1.3"
              />

            <g class="stage-three-range" pointer-events="none">
            <path
              class="range-foothills"
              d="
                M 352 258
                L 400 248
                L 500 234
                L 620 224
                L 740 214
                L 828 208
                L 836 222
                L 740 228
                L 620 238
                L 500 246
                L 400 256
                L 352 266
                Z"
              fill="#b8893d"
              fill-opacity="0.52"
              stroke="#1a1410"
              stroke-width="1"
            />

            <path
              class="range-surface-rim"
              d="M 332 278 L 470 290 L 490 250 L 530 235 L 600 215 L 700 210 L 850 218"
              fill="none"
              stroke="#d4e8ec"
              stroke-width="1.6"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              opacity="0.72"
            />

            <g class="range-peak range-peak--1">
              <path
                d="M 352 266 L 348 240 L 354 210 L 368 182 L 382 210 L 388 240 L 384 266 Z"
                fill="url(#peakG3)"
                stroke="#1a1410"
                stroke-width="1.3"
              />
              <path d="M 368 182 L 378 206 L 374 228 L 364 246 Z" fill="#d4b06a" fill-opacity="0.65"/>
            </g>

            <g class="range-peak range-peak--2">
              <path
                d="M 428 256 L 442 222 L 458 172 L 478 122 L 498 88 L 520 74 L 542 88 L 562 122 L 582 172 L 598 222 L 612 256 L 582 256 L 542 252 L 502 254 L 462 256 L 428 256 Z"
                fill="url(#peakG)"
                stroke="#1a1410"
                stroke-width="1.6"
              />
              <path
                d="M 478 122 L 498 88 L 520 74 L 542 88 L 528 116 L 512 152 L 496 182 L 476 172 Z"
                fill="#e8c47a"
                fill-opacity="0.78"
              />
              <path d="M 442 222 L 458 172 L 478 122 L 498 88 L 520 74 L 542 88 L 562 122 L 582 172" fill="none" stroke="#1a1410" stroke-width="1.3"/>
              <path d="M 498 88 L 520 74 L 542 88 L 528 102 L 514 98 L 504 102 Z" fill="#f1e9d8" fill-opacity="0.9"/>
              <g class="volcanic-smoke" filter="url(#smokeSoft)" aria-hidden="true">
                <path class="smoke-wisp smoke-wisp--1" d="M 518 68 C 512 52, 508 36, 514 22" fill="none" stroke="#8a9098" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.28"/>
                <path class="smoke-wisp smoke-wisp--2" d="M 526 66 C 534 48, 538 30, 530 14" fill="none" stroke="#9aa0a8" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.22"/>
                <path class="smoke-wisp smoke-wisp--3" d="M 522 62 C 520 44, 524 28, 518 10" fill="none" stroke="#7a8088" stroke-width="3.5" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.18"/>
              </g>
            </g>

            <g class="range-peak range-peak--3">
              <path
                d="M 588 242 L 582 210 L 596 176 L 620 150 L 644 176 L 658 210 L 652 242 Z"
                fill="url(#peakG2)"
                stroke="#1a1410"
                stroke-width="1.3"
              />
              <path d="M 620 150 L 630 176 L 626 206 L 612 230 Z" fill="#d4b06a" fill-opacity="0.68"/>
              <path d="M 610 166 L 620 150 L 630 166 L 622 178 Z" fill="#f1e9d8" fill-opacity="0.78"/>
            </g>

